10 An Act relating to schools; creating the Protected
Learning Environment Act; providing short title;
11 stating legislative findings; defining terms;
directing the State Department of Education to
12 develop and publish certain discipline matrix
guidance; requiring the matrix guidance to comply
13 with certain acts; providing for contents of matrix
guidance; requiring school district boards of
14 education to adopt certain matrix based on certain
guidance prior to certain school year; requiring
15 submission of matrix to the Department; requiring
annual review of matrix; requiring school district
16 boards of education to take certain actions;
directing placement of certain student in certain
17 alternative setting; directing school district boards
of education to create certain removal procedures;
18 providing for a student who has committed certain
number of infractions in a semester; requiring
19 documentation of certain incidents; providing for
contents of documentation; providing circumstances
20 under which a teacher may remove a student from
